"""
        Test that a TypeError is raised when an invalid object defaults list
        is used with the DefaultsInformation structure.
        """
kwargs = {'object_defaults': 'invalid'}
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'Object defaults must be a list of ObjectDefaults structures.', objects
    .DefaultsInformation, **kwargs)
args = objects.DefaultsInformation(), 'object_defaults', 'invalid'
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'Object defaults must be a list of ObjectDefaults structures.', setattr,
    *args)
